data.description: Welcome to this exquisite new listing that embodies luxury and comfort in the highly sought after Lindale area. Situated on sprawling 1.9-acre estate, this meticulously designed home offers an unparalleled living experience. Step inside and be greeted by the spacious living room, adorned with a charming fireplace that sets the tone for cozy gatherings and relaxation. The thoughtful layout seamlessly flows into the heart of the home - an elegant eat-in kitchen with a central island, perfect for culinary creations and casual family meals. A convenient pantry ensures ample storage space, catering to your organizational needs. 2023 HVAC with warranty, roof at 4 years old, fresh carpet!   This residence boasts four bedrooms, providing an abundance of private spaces for family members and guests alike. The master bedroom, conveniently located on the lower level, offers a tranquil retreat with its own en-suite bathroom, promising privacy and comfort.  Entertainment reaches new heights in the dedicated media room, where you can indulge in movie nights, gaming adventures, or create a space for your hobbies and interests. The possibilities are endless.  Step outside to discover your personal oasis - an inground gunite pool beckons for refreshing dips on sunny days, surrounded by a fenced and gated perimeter that ensures utmost privacy and security. The 1.9-acre expanse of land provides ample room for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply relishing the serenity of nature.  Car enthusiasts and adventurers will appreciate the convenience of a three-car garage, complete with an RV hook-up, catering to both everyday vehicles and recreational pursuits.  This listing is more than just a home; it's a lifestyle defined by opulence, convenience, and the joy of spacious living. Don't miss the chance to make this extraordinary property your own and experience the epitome of modern elegance. Contact us today for an exclusive tour and the opportunity to embrace a life of luxury.
